CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 21, 1944, p. 13, reads: "LENA TURNS on her famous personality as she cuts the cake at the reception that packed the Loendi Club. The glamorous star formerly lived in Pittsburgh. - Staff Photos by Harris."
TitMainTitle: Lena Horne cutting cake inscribed "Greetings Lena Horne," in Loendi Club, for reception in her honor
